[[File:Chingford War Memorial 07.JPG|thumb|Chingford War Memorial]]

'''Chingford War Memorial''' is a [[listed building|Grade II listed]] war memorial cross at the junction of King's Head Hill and The Ridgeway, [[Chingford]], London, E4.<ref name=EnglishHeritage>{{NHLE |num= 1418307|desc= Chingford War Memorial|access-date= 6 September 2014|mode=cs2}}</ref>

It was unveiled in 1921, and was designed by W. A. Lewis.<ref name=EnglishHeritage/>

